:463744,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:07:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>處理好福島先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無架啦,好似Chernobyl咁等返幾百年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b09f4f84a437d0e4a1c8a761cd0d7dd27b6084b","tid":463744,"uid":7634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:08:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得有得諗, <br />\n香港冇大天災同無地震, <br />\n加上咁多高樓大廈, 中間會有一至兩層隔火層, <br />\n而且天台個使用率奇低, <br />\n<br />\n將個大型機器放係BASEMENT, 隔火層<br />\n重可以善用空間, <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天台個太陽能收集板,做埋個SENOR 跟住個太陽移動, </span><br />\n加上香港位置熱帶地區, 好合適<br />\n<br />\n另外, 化淡都係好岩香港用囉, <br />\n香港三面環海, 根本好多天然資源, <br />\n<br />\n香港唔做科研, 咪請外國專家黎做囉, <br />\n$$$之麻,</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果個摩打唔用電應該先有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSolar tracking仲要每塊版都裝個台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55d566abae7b575a3c5902d2bc7fc7b6cbb0db2","tid":463744,"uid":38523,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電力唔可能俾民間佔有</blockquote><br />\n咁日本係平行時空？<br />\n你地支狗做唔到就話唔可能<br />\n咁又係<br />\n唔係點控制你地班狗"},{"pid":"39f35fee8f29ea8e77eeeddd1f0cafdfc7854c9d","tid":463744,"uid":38523,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:11:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好懷疑報道真實性，大陽能發電效率非常低<br />\n<br />\n2000%又係點黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為你唔撚識字<br />\n自給率同發電率都唔撚識分<br />\n講完"},{"pid":"07d41b142e632748cad21bafc0db091a0d6f0b30","tid":463744,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強國西北d 風車多到發電超載要停用<br />\n小日本做唔做到？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁點解仲要用核電？<br />\n小支狗用下腦啦"},{"pid":"a34ceecc5f2c5bd498396a8586c06dad928e2e31","tid":463744,"uid":7634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:11:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>電力唔可能俾民間佔有</blockquote><br />\n咁日本係平行時空？<br />\n你地支狗做唔到就話唔可能<br />\n咁又係<br />\n唔係點控制你地班狗</blockquote><br />\n人地日本電力市場半open<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ada761c2cb0b4838f8b827ba5b452fff7e88bc","tid":463744,"uid":33605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:12:41.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n成篇文根本冇講到2000%自足率？<br />\n標題黨？<br />\n以我所知日本應該會再起新式核反應堆喎"},{"pid":"059f7b0826eeca05c52a150023cbf3b912baf7f6","tid":463744,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:12:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>電力唔可能俾民間佔有</blockquote><br />\n咁日本係平行時空？<br />\n你地支狗做唔到就話唔可能<br />\n咁又係<br />\n唔係點控制你地班狗</blockquote><br />\n電視節目講外國人間屋都可以有有太陽能,風力,地熱自給自足,有時可以掉轉賣返比電力公司。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16818724886d40f2f8261650c4fb85fc70957eae","tid":463744,"uid":64948,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我好懷疑報道真實性，大陽能發電效率非常低<br />\n<br />\n2000%又係點黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為你唔撚識字<br />\n自給率同發電率都唔撚識分<br />\n講完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地今日教師發展日唔洗返學，晨早起身無野做<br />\n我地體諒下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c08ac015fc3b9afc04526e7cb2d61cd1a24d1ad","tid":463744,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:15:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9<br />\n成篇文根本冇講到2000%自足率？<br />\n標題黨？<br />\n以我所知日本應該會再起新式核反應堆喎</blockquote><br />\n呢篇文應該係吹水,以我所知日本重係要靠核能發電,太陽能效能太低,唯一方法係整幾百支海上風車用風力發電。<br />\n但保養應該好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51917e27e630aac377acf9b5556674e23bd5ff9d","tid":463744,"uid":45350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:20:03.000Z","msg":"d電係賣番比政府/主要電力公司，因為電力係夜晚消耗特別多，民間太陽能板可以係朝早儲起d電，留番夜晚用/賣比人。<br />\n<br />\n至於香港情況，其實依家太陽能板技術advance左好多，香港咁有錢大可以用新ge技術，例如上面講過ge tracking/外牆玻璃式透明太陽能板。亦都有技術係做水上浮台太陽能板，可以善用水塘、河等地方做綠色能源。<br />\n<br />\n其實香港咁撚有錢，政府肯做一定唔比日本台灣差，唔好剩係識話冇地冇資源"},{"pid":"7df1a881b3604dd8f6fd82759e5e27abc7eeeee8","tid":463744,"uid":55712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:21:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我好懷疑報道真實性，大陽能發電效率非常低<br />\n<br />\n2000%又係點黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為你唔撚識字<br />\n自給率同發電率都唔撚識分<br />\n講完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地今日教師發展日唔洗返學，晨早起身無野做<br />\n我地體諒下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心唔識<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f51c1666f0430337d0c8861415808423fc8423","tid":463744,"uid":4180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:24:03.000Z","msg":"柒左一次之後就努力改錯求變，真係幾勁，唔係講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21516509e64c19beb6f279f9647e3609f7c3236","tid":463744,"uid":45591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:26:31.000Z","msg":"日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0c845e7d2adf83ac549e7b16bb63be9cc1d16f","tid":463744,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>太陽能版本身就係污染物</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n信義出果D太陽能板係玻璃黎，應該解決到個污染問題?</blockquote><br />\n發電果 part  應該都係半導體嚟<br />\n生產 同 掉 嘅話對環境有污染</blockquote><br />\n計長遠㗎姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你痾屎都係污染㗎，你生產力高過劈屎咪補償返囉"},{"pid":"e4bec51669117bfaf47d8c0c8ea6751e99d3cf34","tid":463744,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:43:13.000Z","msg":"篇野完全漏撚曬重點，冇錯太陽板發電係得；而且現在有曬先進設備，塊板會跟太陽光轉動。講多個例子你地就估到個問題，又係幾年前，加拿大有條on9諗到租地用太陽板發電賣比水電局，上電視節目抓funding，比人笑。但最後，佢自已攪掂funding，發咗達。你地都估到近十幾年，有乜野發生，蝗國工業生產力爆發，產能過剩；其中一樣係太陽能板。本來環保同人工成本，位on9係唔掂，但蝗國太陽能板平撚到笑，佢先掂。咁你話，唔長遠點可作為公共資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2712cb58c6f1e20730674266c302335baf4e1429","tid":463744,"uid":76728,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:46:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Feed In Tariff  英國都有<br />\n<br />\n不過太陽能係香港應該唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人口密度太高<br />\n即使大廈天台鋪滿太陽能板<br />\n其實夠唔多供應一棟大廈？<br />\n而且每年既檢測修繕費用又要幾多？<br />\n<br />\n連登有無相關專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果好似今年咁打3、4個八號波，我估可以一年換一批板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fdaa0a4b41a1ebee4e6e475b8fd5b64ba671ac6","tid":463744,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:47:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe44726a7584f70ba5f6226f4e0e0dd6aeccd2d3","tid":463744,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>太陽能版本身就係污染物</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n信義出果D太陽能板係玻璃黎，應該解決到個污染問題?</blockquote><br />\n發電果 part  應該都係半導體嚟<br />\n生產 同 掉 嘅話對環境有污染</blockquote><br />\n計長遠㗎姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你痾屎都係污染㗎，你生產力高過劈屎咪補償返囉</blockquote><br />\n我都想見識吓全世界有邊塊太陽能板一生(太陽能板係有壽命)可以cover返生產佢所消耗既能量"},{"pid":"86417497ebb2bbe810474c64def8f77c5898d390","tid":463744,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>太陽能版本身就係污染物</blockquote><br />